       "threading.Condition.__module__.__eq__('threading') == True — Condition is defined in Lib/threading.py; __module__ is 'threading' (len=9: t-h-r-e-a-d-i-n-g); str.__eq__('threading') returns True; verified with Python 3.14.3; new to extra193"]
    - [cond_module_len,
