       true,
       "threading.Condition.__bases__[0].__name__.__eq__('object') == True — Condition inherits directly from object with no intermediary base class; __bases__[0].__name__ is 'object'; str.__eq__('object') returns True; verified with Python 3.14.3; new to extra193"]

